Inspired by the iconic Indian drink, Jaljeera, this frozen delight offers a unique twist on a beloved classic. Indulge in the perfect balance of tanginess and sweetness. Havmor's Jaljeera Ice Candy offers a taste sensation that will leave you craving more.

products.desc: Havmor's Kala Khatta Ice Candy: Bursting with aromatic spices, each bite promises a nostalgic delight. It's the perfect companion for hot summer days or any moment of indulgence. Experience the essence of tradition with Havmor's Kala Khatta Ice Candy.

products.title: Choco Crunch Shotties
products.desc: A shot of crunchy chocolate that will delight your senses without making you feel guilty! The Choco Crunch is packed with rich, smooth and delicious flavour, we call it happiness in a bite.

products.title: DARK CHOCOLATE SHOTTIES
products.desc: A bite-sized treat for dark chocolate lovers! You know those moments when you’re just craving for something sweet but don’t know what to eat? The Dark Chocolate Shotties is the perfect solution for that.

products.title: Taj Mahal
products.desc: Pamper your taste buds with the most regal ice cream of them all. Rich, creamy and delectable ice cream with generous sprinklings of cashews, almonds and figs and blended with aromatic rose petals and gulkand.

products.title: PREMIUM BUTTER SCOTCH
products.desc: The Butterscotch ice cream gets an opulent upgrade for pleasure seekers looking for pure indulgence. With the goodness of real cashews, its rich and creamy taste will satisfy all your sweet tooth cravings.

products.title: AMERICAN MUD CAKE
products.desc: Sinfully delicious, the American Mud Cake ice cream combines chocolate fudge and ice cream with a burst of brownie pieces in every bite.

products.title: CREAM OREO WAFFLE SUNDAE
products.desc: Whether you are hosting guests or just having a fun family night together, the Cream Oreo Waffle Sundae is the perfect dessert to serve! Get a waffle topped with rich chocolate ice cream, the deliciousness of Oreo biscuits and your favourite toppings.

products.title: CHOCOLATE OVERLOAD WAFFLE SUNDAE
products.desc: Chocolate lovers, this sinful Waffle Sundae is for you! A scoop of the most delightful chocolate ice cream served on a waffle, topped with cream and drizzled with a generous splash of chocolate sauce and choco chips as the finishing touch. Yum!

products.title: BERRY MAGIC WAFFLE SUNDAE
products.desc: For a refreshing summer dessert, we recommend the Berry Magic Waffle Sundae. It’s got the luscious combination of strawberries, blueberries and cranberries all scooped together on a waffle. Fresh cream, syrup and literal cherries on top make this sundae even more delightful!

products.title: AMERICAN NUT FUN WAFFLE SUNDAE
products.desc: Our American Nuts ice cream gets a “fun” upgrade with our American Nut Fun Waffle Sundae. Two scoops of ice cream sandwiched between two waffle slices, this is a party treat made in dessert heaven!

products.title: STRAWBERRY STUNNER
products.desc: Creamy, dreamy and full of flavour! Ice cream packed with the flavour of fresh strawberries, served in a waffle cone and topped with a waffle biscuit, fresh cream and nuts. Treat your senses to a delightful experience with the Strawberry Stunner.

products.title: SIZZLING BROWNIE VOLCANO
products.desc: This one’s a crowd pleaser! For those who like their dessert hot and cold, try this explosion of flavours on a platter. The most decadent brownie, served with a scoop of vanilla ice cream and topped off with chocolate sauce.
